---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="公积金提取 - 广西房产金融服务">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">公积金提取</h1>
      <p class="text-xl">购房 | 租房 | 装修 | 离职 | 全方位服务</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">提取类型</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">🏠 购房提取</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">购买商品房、二手房可提取公积金支付首付或偿还贷款</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">🏡 租房提取</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">无房职工可提取公积金支付租金</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">🔧 装修提取</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">自住房屋装修可提取公积金</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">💼 离职提取</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">离职封存满半年可提取公积金</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">申请条件</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-12">
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 连续缴存公积金6个月以上</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 信用记录良好</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 符合提取条件</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-accent mr-2">✓</span> 材料准备齐全</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">所需材料</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl mb-12">
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>📋 身份证原件及复印件</li>
          <li>📋 公积金卡</li>
          <li>📋 相关证明材料（购房合同、租房合同等）</li>
          <li>📋 婚姻状况证明</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">我们的优势</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl text-accent mb-4">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">快速审批</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">3-5个工作日到账</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl text-accent mb-4">📝</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">材料简化</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">一次准备齐全</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="text-4xl text-accent mb-4">💯</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">额度优化</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">最大化提取额度</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">立即预约免费咨询</h3>
        <a href="tel:17200861361" class="btn-primary text-lg px-10">📞 172-0086-1361</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>